flowchart LR
    Browser[Browser\nNext pages + in-memory access JWT]

    subgraph Edge[Application edge]
        Nginx[Nginx reverse proxy]
    end

    subgraph Frontend[Frontend]
        Next[Next.js App Router\nport 3000]
        BFF[Same-origin BFF\n/api/proxy/*]
    end

    subgraph Backend[Django services]
        Daphne[Django REST + Channels\nDaphne port 8000]
        Migrate[One-shot migrate + collectstatic]
        Worker[Celery worker]
        Beat[Celery beat]
    end

    subgraph State[Data and storage]
        Postgres[(PostgreSQL)]
        Redis[(Redis cache + broker)]
        Static[Collected static]
        PublicMedia[Public media]
        PrivateMedia[Private media / S3]
    end

    subgraph External[Optional external services]
        Razorpay[Razorpay\nwhen PAYMENT_MODE=online]
        Email[Email provider]
        SMS[SMS / OTP provider]
    end

    Browser -->|/, /_next/*| Nginx
    Browser -->|same-origin API| Nginx
    Browser -->|/ws/* subprotocol auth| Nginx
    Nginx -->|pages and assets| Next
    Next --> BFF
    BFF -->|server-to-server /api/v1/*| Daphne
    Nginx -->|/api/*, /django-admin/*| Daphne
    Nginx -->|WebSocket upgrade| Daphne
    Nginx -->|/static/*| Static
    Nginx -->|public /media/*| PublicMedia

    Migrate --> Postgres
    Migrate --> Static
    Daphne --> Postgres
    Daphne --> Redis
    Daphne --> PrivateMedia
    Worker --> Redis
    Worker --> Postgres
    Beat --> Redis
    Daphne --> Razorpay
    Daphne --> Email
    Daphne --> SMS
